com.zpaper.kbapp.model

Class KBDataWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zpaper.kbapp.model.KBDataWrapper

  • public class KBDataWrapper
extends Object
    This is a simple wrapper class that turns KBData into more of a Java bean. It hides the public member variables in KBData and makes them available via getters/setters. User: Cory Date: 4/18/14 Time: 12:28 PM
